Kenyan Telecoms Regulator Won't Renew DG's Contract, Business Daily Says

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-03-15T04:01:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/kenyan-telecoms-regulator-won-t-renew-dg-s-contract-business-daily-says.html
The Communications Commission of  Kenya ’s board recommended against renewing Director-General
Charles Njoroge’s contract, Business Daily reported, citing
people it didn’t identify.  Njoroge had requested in December that his contract be
renewed for three years, the Nairobi-based newspaper said.  Njoroge didn’t answer his mobile phone when called this
morning by Bloomberg News for comment.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  